reviewText: great...not the quality expected as live at beach so lots of background noixe and people walking by....but the instruction was good and I led a class using it and the guest enjoyed that.

Quite helpful in getting a grasp of the basic elements for a laughter yoga session in keeping with the guidelines of its founder, Dr. Kataria. If you can't go to the west coast and participate in person, this is a great chance to see Jeffrey (one of the leading laughter yoga practitioners/master teachers in the U.S.) and his long-standing, well-known laughter club members in action :).
